snippet.title: GOD EATER 3 - OVA Trailer | PS4, PC
snippet.description:
Turn up the sound and rock out to the Cinematic Opening for GOD EATER 3! 

Rise above a world of desolation in GOD EATER 3, coming to PS4 and Steam on February 8, 2019. Pre-order your copy today: https://bandainam.co/GE3PO #BandaiNamco #GodEater #GodEater3
